---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Nav from '../components/Nav.astro';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="RAE Partners" 
  description="Responsible Autonomous Engineering. We help organizations deploy AI coding agents reliably and hold them accountable to high-quality outcomes."
>
  <Nav />
  
  <main class="pt-24">
    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 md:py-32">
      <div class="text-center">
        <h1 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl font-bold tracking-tight text-foreground mb-6">
          Responsible Autonomous Engineering
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl md:text-2xl text-muted-foreground max-w-2xl mx-auto mb-8 leading-relaxed">
          We help organizations deploy AI coding agents reliably and hold them accountable to high-quality outcomes.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a 
            href="mailto:hello@rae.partners" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors"
          >
            Get in touch
          </a>
          <a 
            href="/blog" 
            class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-6 py-3 text-base font-medium rounded-md border border-border bg-background hover:bg-muted transition-colors"
          >
            Read our thinking
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- Brief Intro Section -->
    <section class="bg-muted/30 border-y border-border">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
        <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto text-center">
          <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-6">
            The robots are ready. Are you?
          </h2>
          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed mb-6">
            2026 is the year hands-off, eyes-off autonomous engineering becomes possible for mature organizations. But only for those who learn how to hold agentic coding tools and their operators accountable to high-quality outcomes.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground leading-relaxed">
            We&apos;ve spent years figuring out how to manage dozens of AI coding agents working simultaneously, reliably producing software that exceeds product and engineering expectations. Our battle-hardened tools and practices are finally ready to share.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- What We Believe Section -->
    <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
      <div class="max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-8 text-center">
          What unlocks autonomous engineering
        </h2>
        <div class="grid gap-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-foreground">Thoroughly-documented code</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Agents need context to make good decisions.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-foreground">Comprehensive automated tests</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">The only reliable way to verify agent output at scale.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-foreground">Well-supported modern frameworks</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Agents work best with patterns in their training data.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-foreground">Rigorously-researched technical specifications</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Clear requirements prevent agents from spinning.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-foreground">Production-equivalent development environments</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Reduce the gap between agent output and production reality.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
            <div class="w-2 h-2 rounded-full bg-accent mt-2.5 shrink-0"></div>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-medium text-foreground">Infrastructure as Code</h3>
              <p class="text-muted-foreground">Reproducible environments agents can understand and modify.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="mt-8 text-center text-muted-foreground">
          The good news? Agentic coding tools, paired with well-trained architects, can bootstrap these best practices in weeks, not years.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>
    
    <!-- CTA Section -->
    <section class="bg-primary/5 border-y border-border">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 text-center">
        <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-semibold text-foreground mb-4">
          Ready to build software better and faster?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-muted-foreground mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          Whether you want to deploy autonomous engineering or help us build the tools, we&apos;d love to partner with you.
        </p>
        <a 
          href="mailto:hello@rae.partners" 
          class="inline-flex items-center justify-center px-8 py-4 text-lg font-medium rounded-md bg-primary text-primary-foreground hover:bg-primary/90 transition-colors"
        >
          Let&apos;s talk
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
  
  <Footer />
</BaseLayout>
